1
00:00:05,870 --> 00:00:11,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Hellhorde and Imperial Army have been 
locked in battle for many years.</i></font>

2
00:00:11,830 --> 00:00:15,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Led by their grand inquisitor, 
Torture Tortura,</i></font>

3
00:00:15,500 --> 00:00:18,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the Hellhorde's elite inflict 
their torture on a daily basis.</i></font>

4
00:00:18,650 --> 00:00:23,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She faces fierce beasts, flames, 
unknown devices and spells,</i></font>

5
00:00:23,420 --> 00:00:26,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>yet the princess does not give in.</i></font>

6
00:00:26,330 --> 00:00:28,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She would never give in.</i></font>

7
00:00:28,250 --> 00:00:32,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She would never let the words, 
"I surrender!" leave her lips so readily.</i></font>

8
00:00:32,920 --> 00:00:38,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Meanwhile, the princess's former friend, 
the assassin Sakura Heartrock,</i></font>

9
00:00:38,680 --> 00:00:44,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>fails to assassinate the Hell-Lord, 
and sets off on a new path.</i></font>

10
00:00:45,980 --> 00:00:49,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Tis time for torture, Princess...</font>

11
00:00:51,980 --> 00:00:54,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is what I'd usually say, but...</font>

12
00:01:05,450 --> 00:01:09,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we have Hellholm Pre-School joining us 
today for Bring a Kid to Work Day.</font>

13
00:01:09,940 --> 00:01:11,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bring a Kid to Work Day?!</font>

14
00:01:11,970 --> 00:01:16,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you going to make 
these children torture me?!</font>

15
00:01:16,840 --> 00:01:18,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All together now!</font>

16
00:01:18,340 --> 00:01:20,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Princess!</font>

17
00:01:20,180 --> 00:01:26,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks a lot for having us today!</font>

18
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:29,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're all raring to go!</font>

19
00:01:29,810 --> 00:01:31,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope I have enough secrets for you all.</font>

20
00:01:31,720 --> 00:01:32,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness?</font>

21
00:01:33,160 --> 00:01:34,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen, Ex.</font>

22
00:01:34,460 --> 00:01:38,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thinking about it, I give in to 
Maomao-chan when she's by herself,</font>

23
00:01:38,620 --> 00:01:41,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I never stood a chance 
against so many of them.</font>

24
00:01:42,210 --> 00:01:44,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop with the calm self-evaluation.</font>

25
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:51,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Today, we'll show you a torture 
we practiced very hard!</font>

26
00:01:52,880 --> 00:01:57,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We hope that you enjoy it!</font>

27
00:01:57,870 --> 00:01:59,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure!</font>

28
00:03:28,220 --> 00:03:29,980
<font size="20"><b><font color="#d01c76">{\an8}<font size="32">'Tis Time for <font color="#020000">"Torture,"
<font color="#cf1374">Princess</font></font></font></font></b></font>

29
00:03:33,930 --> 00:03:38,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The kids from Hellholm Pre-School 
will be performing on handbells.</font>

30
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:41,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-one, a-two...</font>

31
00:04:17,270 --> 00:04:20,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for listening!</font>

32
00:04:23,110 --> 00:04:25,820
<font size="20"><font size="15"><b><font color="#1a191c">{\an8}The princess
confessed</font></b></font></font>

33
00:04:26,060 --> 00:04:30,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems that the first word 
that the princess ever spoke was "bread."</font>

34
00:04:30,420 --> 00:04:35,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maomao-chan's first word was "Mama."</font>

35
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:38,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On that note, I hear today's torture...</font>

36
00:04:38,430 --> 00:04:45,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">was a spectacular handbell performance 
put on by Maomao-chan and her friends.</font>

37
00:04:45,330 --> 00:04:46,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's correct.</font>

38
00:04:46,760 --> 00:04:50,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And? Where's the video?</font>

39
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:52,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? A video?</font>

40
00:04:52,490 --> 00:04:58,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We didn't receive a video, 
so I don't believe it was recorded.</font>

41
00:04:58,260 --> 00:04:59,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

42
00:05:02,290 --> 00:05:03,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-It can't be...</font>

43
00:05:03,910 --> 00:05:08,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean I can't see 
Maomao-chan playing handbells?</font>

44
00:05:11,590 --> 00:05:12,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Majesty?!</font>

45
00:05:13,770 --> 00:05:16,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Majesty!</font>

46
00:05:21,780 --> 00:05:24,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Hell-Lord passed away.</i></font>

47
00:05:24,420 --> 00:05:26,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, he's not dead.</font>

48
00:05:26,940 --> 00:05:31,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, the shock of missing 
Princess Maomao-chan playing handbells</font>

49
00:05:31,940 --> 00:05:33,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">has made him inconsolable.</font>

50
00:05:33,410 --> 00:05:34,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Papa's in a funk.</font>

51
00:05:35,420 --> 00:05:38,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's so bummed out, 
his horns are drooping.</font>

52
00:05:38,850 --> 00:05:41,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My apologies for not recording a video.</font>

53
00:05:41,670 --> 00:05:45,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were just busy 
doing your job, Torture.</font>

54
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:48,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, to cheer Go-chan up,</font>

55
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:53,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we'll ask the Hellholm Pre-School kids 
to put on another handbell show!</font>

56
00:05:53,350 --> 00:05:54,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

57
00:05:54,570 --> 00:05:58,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Hell-Lord's wife 
calls him "Go-chan."</i></font>

58
00:05:58,710 --> 00:06:02,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The other preschoolers 
have agreed to help us out.</font>

59
00:06:03,370 --> 00:06:09,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But a normal performance would be boring, 
so we'll make it a surprise.</font>

60
00:06:09,910 --> 00:06:11,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I call it...</font>

61
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:15,180
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="25"><font color="#545757">Operation: Handbell Flash Mob!!</font></font></font></b></font>

62
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:15,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Operation: Handbell Flash Mob!</font>

63
00:06:15,520 --> 00:06:19,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First, we'll get a secret 
out of the princess as usual,</font>

64
00:06:19,190 --> 00:06:21,690
<font size="20"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="23"><font color="#474947">Papa</font></font></font></b></font>

65
00:06:19,190 --> 00:06:21,690
<font size="20"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="23"><font color="#474947">Kanadge</font></font></font></b></font>

66
00:06:19,190 --> 00:06:21,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and have Kanadge report it.</font>

67
00:06:21,990 --> 00:06:24,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When suddenly, Kanadge...</font>

68
00:06:23,190 --> 00:06:24,820
<font size="20"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="23"><font color="#333533">Kanadge</font></font></font></b></font>

69
00:06:25,100 --> 00:06:27,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've failed to extract a secret 
from the princess.</font>

70
00:06:27,970 --> 00:06:28,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or so he says!</font>

71
00:06:28,900 --> 00:06:30,660
<font size="20"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#2f322f">Huh?!</font></font></b></font>

72
00:06:29,200 --> 00:06:30,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which alarms Papa!</font>

73
00:06:31,060 --> 00:06:34,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The torture has failed?</font>

74
00:06:35,510 --> 00:06:39,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is Torture not feeling 
like herself, either?</font>

75
00:06:39,780 --> 00:06:41,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then!</font>

76
00:06:41,370 --> 00:06:43,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Upbeat music starts 
playing out of nowhere!</font>

77
00:06:45,900 --> 00:06:49,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Is that music I hear?</font>

78
00:06:51,130 --> 00:06:54,220
<font size="20"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="20"><font color="#333533">Kanadge</font></font></font></b></font>

79
00:06:51,340 --> 00:06:54,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kanadge starts dancing along to the beat!</font>

80
00:07:01,940 --> 00:07:05,400
<font size="20"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#525552">Woo-hoo</font></font></b></font>

81
00:07:02,220 --> 00:07:05,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In come the preschoolers 
and their guardians!</font>

82
00:07:10,220 --> 00:07:11,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What in the world?</font>

83
00:07:12,310 --> 00:07:13,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on?</font>

84
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:17,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then the handbell show!</font>

85
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:20,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let us begin the handbell performance.</font>

86
00:07:24,100 --> 00:07:25,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-one, a-two...</font>

87
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:03,250
<font size="20"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="18"><font color="#474947">Papa</font></font></font></b></font>

88
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:02,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Papa's moved to tears!</font>

89
00:08:03,630 --> 00:08:06,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for listening!</font>

90
00:08:11,870 --> 00:08:14,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was incredible!</font>

91
00:08:14,590 --> 00:08:17,550
<font size="20"><font size="15"><b><font color="#1a191c">{\an8}The Hell-Lord cheered up</font></b></font></font>

92
00:08:17,550 --> 00:08:22,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Lulune had always wanted to 
try her hand at a flash mob.</i></font>

93
00:08:22,590 --> 00:08:28,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And she believes that it's not 
a flash mob unless there's dancing.</i></font>

94
00:08:33,820 --> 00:08:37,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it okay if I go out for the night?</font>

95
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:40,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's dangerous to go out at night!</font>

96
00:08:40,430 --> 00:08:41,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it some kind of event?</font>

97
00:08:42,410 --> 00:08:46,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You see, they're holding 
a festival tonight.</font>

98
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:50,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was thinking of inviting a friend.</font>

99
00:08:50,680 --> 00:08:52,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say no more!</font>

100
00:08:52,790 --> 00:08:54,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go enjoy yourselves!</font>

101
00:08:56,190 --> 00:08:57,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

102
00:08:59,410 --> 00:09:03,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She should be done with
today's torture right about now.</i></font>

103
00:09:03,850 --> 00:09:08,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I didn't make it very clear last time, 
but I'll invite her properly today.</i></font>

104
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:11,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get to go to the festival 
with you, Vanilla-chan?</font>

105
00:09:11,710 --> 00:09:13,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so happy!</font>

106
00:09:13,230 --> 00:09:16,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The princess is sure 
to be overcome with joy!</i></font>

107
00:09:18,930 --> 00:09:21,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I even got some allowance money.</i></font>

108
00:09:21,810 --> 00:09:23,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't wait.</i></font>

109
00:09:24,670 --> 00:09:27,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've delivered our report 
to the grand inquisitor!</font>

110
00:09:27,710 --> 00:09:29,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That means we're done with you.</font>

111
00:09:29,920 --> 00:09:31,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it...</font>

112
00:09:31,400 --> 00:09:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, get a hold of yourself!</font>

113
00:09:33,770 --> 00:09:36,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Looks like the torture's just ended.</i></font>

114
00:09:36,370 --> 00:09:37,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Princess—</font>

115
00:09:36,770 --> 00:09:38,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Oh yeah, Princess-chan.</font>

116
00:09:38,540 --> 00:09:41,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a festival tonight. 
Wanna come with us?</font>

117
00:09:42,510 --> 00:09:44,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Really?</font>

118
00:09:44,220 --> 00:09:46,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I'm down!</font>

119
00:09:45,250 --> 00:09:46,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Awesome!</font>

120
00:09:46,500 --> 00:09:47,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's great!</font>

121
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:49,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What food do you think they'll sell?</font>

122
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:50,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I hope there's shaved ice.</font>

123
00:09:50,660 --> 00:09:52,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds good! And takoyaki's a must!</font>

124
00:09:52,710 --> 00:09:54,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's always tasty!</font>

125
00:09:57,480 --> 00:10:01,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Right. I forgot the princess is popular.</i></font>

126
00:10:01,580 --> 00:10:04,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Makes sense that someone else 
would invite her.</i></font>

127
00:10:06,370 --> 00:10:08,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I messed up.</i></font>

128
00:10:08,330 --> 00:10:11,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I should have called her 
to ask beforehand.</i></font>

129
00:10:11,610 --> 00:10:13,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That'd be the right move.</i></font>

130
00:10:15,870 --> 00:10:18,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I always mess up...</i></font>

131
00:10:19,180 --> 00:10:21,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Papa. Mama.</i></font>

132
00:10:22,070 --> 00:10:27,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm sure they'd be sad 
if they knew how I felt right now.</i></font>

133
00:10:34,300 --> 00:10:35,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My phone!</font>

134
00:10:37,540 --> 00:10:39,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, Vanilla-chan!</i></font>

135
00:10:39,830 --> 00:10:42,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All of us are about to 
head out to the festival.</font>

136
00:10:42,620 --> 00:10:44,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want to join us?</font>

137
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:47,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

138
00:10:50,540 --> 00:10:52,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everything looks so good.</font>

139
00:10:56,150 --> 00:10:57,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Delish!</font>

140
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:00,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So hot!</font>

141
00:11:10,700 --> 00:11:12,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey there!</font>

142
00:11:24,700 --> 00:11:25,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Almost!</font>

143
00:11:25,910 --> 00:11:27,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Too bad.</font>

144
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:28,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a shame.</font>

145
00:11:40,580 --> 00:11:43,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know what color I want, 
but it looks hard to get.</font>

146
00:11:44,070 --> 00:11:45,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave it to me!</font>

147
00:11:45,810 --> 00:11:48,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As the daughter of the
noble House of Peschutz,</font>

148
00:11:48,760 --> 00:11:51,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm great at water balloon fishing.</font>

149
00:12:14,810 --> 00:12:17,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're amazing, Vanilla-chan!</font>

150
00:12:20,730 --> 00:12:22,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm back!</font>

151
00:12:22,910 --> 00:12:24,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're back?</font>

152
00:12:24,100 --> 00:12:25,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome home.</font>

153
00:12:25,970 --> 00:12:28,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have fun at the festival?</font>

154
00:12:28,820 --> 00:12:31,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah! I had a great time!</font>

155
00:12:34,940 --> 00:12:36,980
<font size="20"><b><font color="#d01c76">{\an8}<font size="22">'Tis Time for <font color="#020000">"Torture,"
<font color="#cf1374">Princess</font></font></font></font></b></font>

156
00:12:36,980 --> 00:12:39,360
<font size="20"><font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#4c332f">Shooting Gallery</font></b></font></font>

157
00:12:38,230 --> 00:12:41,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Princess-chan, time for some torture!</font>

158
00:12:41,600 --> 00:12:44,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Today's torture is a shooting gallery.</font>

159
00:12:44,520 --> 00:12:47,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Each prize has a point 
value based on its size.</font>

160
00:12:44,530 --> 00:12:52,830
<font size="20"><font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#4c332f">{\an8}Shooting Gallery</font></b></font></font>

161
00:12:44,530 --> 00:12:52,830
<font size="20"><b><font color="#2e1625"><font size="15">Guy running
the stall</font></font></b></font>

162
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:52,830
<font size="20"><b><font color="#462331"><font size="15">1 point</font></font></b></font>

163
00:12:46,820 --> 00:12:52,830
<font size="20"><b><font color="#301721"><font size="15">3 points</font></font></b></font>

164
00:12:47,320 --> 00:12:52,830
<font size="20"><b><font color="#321627"><font size="15">5 points</font></font></b></font>

165
00:12:47,910 --> 00:12:52,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll each get five rounds, 
and whoever gets more points wins.</font>

166
00:12:53,550 --> 00:12:55,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A shooting gallery?</font>

167
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:58,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never been great with guns.</font>

168
00:12:59,630 --> 00:13:02,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's information we already have!</font>

169
00:13:02,060 --> 00:13:02,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

170
00:13:03,090 --> 00:13:05,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, I'm really good.</font>

171
00:13:07,070 --> 00:13:09,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That look of confidence 
on Youki's face...</font>

172
00:13:09,520 --> 00:13:11,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're in trouble, Your Highness!</font>

173
00:13:11,610 --> 00:13:14,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. This won't be an easy fight.</font>

174
00:13:16,240 --> 00:13:19,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. I'll be going first.</font>

175
00:13:20,260 --> 00:13:23,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Behold my superb sharpshooting technique!</font>

176
00:13:25,270 --> 00:13:25,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hah!</font>

177
00:13:26,900 --> 00:13:27,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmph!</font>

178
00:13:28,400 --> 00:13:28,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There!</font>

179
00:13:29,910 --> 00:13:30,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bam!</font>

180
00:13:32,450 --> 00:13:36,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One plus three makes four points.</font>

181
00:13:37,160 --> 00:13:38,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pretty normal.</font>

182
00:13:38,650 --> 00:13:39,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not very impressive.</font>

183
00:13:39,830 --> 00:13:40,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

184
00:13:41,280 --> 00:13:45,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the festival hero if you manage 
to win two prizes at the shooting gallery!</font>

185
00:13:46,220 --> 00:13:50,590
<font size="20"><font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#42302b">Shooting Gallery</font></b></font></font>

186
00:13:46,610 --> 00:13:49,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next! You're up, Princess-chan.</font>

187
00:13:49,150 --> 00:13:50,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

188
00:13:56,560 --> 00:13:59,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, I'll set my sights on that plushie.</font>

189
00:14:03,060 --> 00:14:04,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoops...</font>

190
00:14:04,520 --> 00:14:06,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't even get close.</font>

191
00:14:07,980 --> 00:14:09,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like an easy win for me.</font>

192
00:14:17,800 --> 00:14:19,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She grazed it!</font>

193
00:14:19,510 --> 00:14:21,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Almost.</font>

194
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, I have the hang of it now.</font>

195
00:14:22,970 --> 00:14:26,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-How'd you land a hit so easily?</font>

196
00:14:26,970 --> 00:14:28,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

197
00:14:28,170 --> 00:14:31,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I worked out the trajectory from 
where the first bullet hit,</font>

198
00:14:31,020 --> 00:14:32,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and fine-tuned my aim a bit.</font>

199
00:14:32,630 --> 00:14:34,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

200
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:36,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Last night at the shooting gallery 
was just child's play.</i></font>

201
00:14:36,860 --> 00:14:40,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now that it's a showdown, 
Princess-chan's in serious mode.</i></font>

202
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:43,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No more taking advantage of weaknesses 
when it's what they do for a living!</font>

203
00:14:44,410 --> 00:14:46,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We're talking about Princess-chan here.</i></font>

204
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:48,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She might really get it on her next shot.</i></font>

205
00:14:49,150 --> 00:14:50,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But too bad.</i></font>

206
00:14:50,650 --> 00:14:54,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The five-point prizes 
are actually clamped in place!</i></font>

207
00:14:54,470 --> 00:14:59,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I figured she'd aim for 
the big prizes based on her personality,</i></font>

208
00:14:59,080 --> 00:15:01,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and used that to plant a trap.</i></font>

209
00:15:01,340 --> 00:15:06,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And even if Princess-chan gets 
suspicious and tries to check...</i></font>

210
00:15:06,510 --> 00:15:10,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The clamps are set up to release
with the press of a button.</i></font>

211
00:15:10,440 --> 00:15:13,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>With the button on the
pole facing the stall owner.</i></font>

212
00:15:14,090 --> 00:15:17,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If he releases them before she 
can check, she'll never find out.</i></font>

213
00:15:18,640 --> 00:15:22,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yes, the shooting gallery 
owner is in on it, too.</i></font>

214
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:24,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Well, actually...</i></font>

215
00:15:24,360 --> 00:15:27,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>he's Vanilla, disguised using magic!</i></font>

216
00:15:28,120 --> 00:15:30,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Too bad, Princess-chan.</i></font>

217
00:15:30,680 --> 00:15:33,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The moment you agreed 
to this shooting gallery torture,</i></font>

218
00:15:33,750 --> 00:15:36,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>your fate was already decided!</i></font>

219
00:15:36,880 --> 00:15:38,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness.</font>

220
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:40,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Instead of going for the five-pointer,</font>

221
00:15:40,150 --> 00:15:42,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">wouldn't it be safer to go 
for the three and one-pointers?</font>

222
00:15:42,870 --> 00:15:43,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

223
00:15:43,920 --> 00:15:44,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Uh oh!</i></font>

224
00:15:45,350 --> 00:15:50,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those plushies look heavy, 
so they might not fall even with a hit.</font>

225
00:15:50,270 --> 00:15:51,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

226
00:15:51,420 --> 00:15:53,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shoot to break its balance 
with the center of gravity in mind,</font>

227
00:15:53,920 --> 00:15:55,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and it has a chance of falling over.</font>

228
00:15:56,080 --> 00:15:58,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you so insistent on that one?</font>

229
00:15:58,450 --> 00:16:01,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop being stubborn 
and aim for safer ways to win!</font>

230
00:16:04,460 --> 00:16:06,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still...</font>

231
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:10,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That plushie's a character 
that Vanilla-chan likes.</font>

232
00:16:11,070 --> 00:16:14,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought she'd be happy 
if I won it for her.</font>

233
00:16:17,420 --> 00:16:19,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Princess!</i></font>

234
00:16:21,410 --> 00:16:23,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was scared for a minute, but I'm saved!</i></font>

235
00:16:23,910 --> 00:16:26,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Princess-chan's going for the plushie!</i></font>

236
00:16:26,870 --> 00:16:28,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's no use, Princess-chan.</i></font>

237
00:16:28,580 --> 00:16:32,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even if you land a bull's-eye, 
that plushie will never fall!</i></font>

238
00:16:32,820 --> 00:16:36,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So long as Vanilla doesn't 
press the release button!</i></font>

239
00:16:36,720 --> 00:16:37,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

240
00:16:38,040 --> 00:16:40,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did I just hear a beep from 
the button being pressed?</i></font>

241
00:16:41,130 --> 00:16:43,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Vanilla? Did you press it?</i></font>

242
00:16:44,720 --> 00:16:45,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Vanilla?</i></font>

243
00:16:45,960 --> 00:16:49,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why are you making goo-goo eyes 
at Princess-chan?</i></font>

244
00:16:51,230 --> 00:16:53,940
<font size="20"><font size="14"><b><font color="#353438">{\an8}The princess won</font></b></font></font>

245
00:16:53,940 --> 00:16:57,950
<font size="20"><b><font color="#d01c76">{\an8}<font size="22">'Tis Time for <font color="#020000">"Torture,"
<font color="#cf1374">Princess</font></font></font></font></b></font>

246
00:16:53,940 --> 00:16:57,950
<font size="20"><b><font color="#af60dc">{\an7}A Hit in the Demon World
<font size="35"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#e866ad">Loose-Lipz 
<font size="15"><font face="Arial"><font color="#7355a8"></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></b>A character who's a hit in the demon world
Loves to talk and has its mouth sewn shut</font>

247
00:17:03,400 --> 00:17:07,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm so happy that I managed 
to find a four-leaf clover.</i></font>

248
00:17:08,750 --> 00:17:11,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now I can torture the princess with this!</i></font>

249
00:17:15,590 --> 00:17:16,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's...</i></font>

250
00:17:17,360 --> 00:17:21,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I believe she recently 
became a pain-private.</i></font>

251
00:17:21,470 --> 00:17:22,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sakura.</i></font>

252
00:17:23,180 --> 00:17:25,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It looks like something's bothering her.</i></font>

253
00:17:26,700 --> 00:17:28,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Maybe I should ask her about it.</i></font>

254
00:17:28,800 --> 00:17:32,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've never talked 
to her in private, though.</i></font>

255
00:17:33,670 --> 00:17:36,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm too nervous to do it.</i></font>

256
00:17:36,120 --> 00:17:37,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Time to run away.</i></font>

257
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:51,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If it was the princess, 
I'm sure she'd say something.</i></font>

258
00:17:58,440 --> 00:17:59,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sakura.</font>

259
00:18:00,420 --> 00:18:03,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's with the long face?</font>

260
00:18:04,030 --> 00:18:05,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're...</font>

261
00:18:05,750 --> 00:18:12,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall I, Vanilla Peschutz, daughter of
the noble House of Peschutz, lend an ear?</font>

262
00:18:12,240 --> 00:18:13,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I managed to talk to her!</i></font>

263
00:18:14,280 --> 00:18:15,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vanilla-senpai...</font>

264
00:18:16,480 --> 00:18:18,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please listen to me.</font>

265
00:18:18,620 --> 00:18:22,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll finally be performing 
my first torture next week.</font>

266
00:18:23,070 --> 00:18:27,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm worried because I'm not sure 
if my torture will be good enough.</font>

267
00:18:30,220 --> 00:18:32,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Senpai?</font>

268
00:18:32,760 --> 00:18:34,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you hear me?</font>

269
00:18:34,390 --> 00:18:36,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vanilla-senpai?</font>

270
00:18:36,250 --> 00:18:40,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vanilla-senpai? Senpai? Senpai?</font>

271
00:18:40,250 --> 00:18:42,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Senpai?!</i></font>

272
00:18:42,600 --> 00:18:50,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Hooray! Yay!</i></font>

273
00:18:42,600 --> 00:18:46,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Since I skipped grades in school, 
everyone around me's always been older.</i></font>

274
00:18:46,330 --> 00:18:49,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've never been called "Senpai" before!</i></font>

275
00:18:49,470 --> 00:18:51,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm so happy!</i></font>

276
00:18:51,860 --> 00:18:53,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand!</font>

277
00:18:53,050 --> 00:18:58,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As your <i>senpai,</i> I'll help 
you come up with tortures!</font>

278
00:18:58,590 --> 00:19:00,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since I'm your <i>senpai</i> and all!</font>

279
00:19:00,530 --> 00:19:03,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? You mean it?</font>

280
00:19:05,980 --> 00:19:08,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First, show me what you can do, Sakura.</font>

281
00:19:08,830 --> 00:19:09,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

282
00:19:10,830 --> 00:19:15,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I used to be an assassin, 
so I've got good hand dexterity.</font>

283
00:19:15,920 --> 00:19:17,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can take a Rubik's Cube...</font>

284
00:19:17,550 --> 00:19:19,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">hit it with pebbles from afar...</font>

285
00:19:25,720 --> 00:19:27,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and solve all six sides.</font>

286
00:19:28,420 --> 00:19:30,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have good stamina as well.</font>

287
00:19:31,040 --> 00:19:33,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can run fifty kilometers 
in around two hours.</font>

288
00:19:34,220 --> 00:19:37,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I speak nine languages
so I can go undercover.</font>

289
00:19:37,570 --> 00:19:40,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My engineering knowledge means 
I can assemble a car from its parts.</font>

290
00:19:40,770 --> 00:19:43,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, my taste buds have been trained,</font>

291
00:19:43,850 --> 00:19:46,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">allowing me to figure out 
the ingredients by trying a dish.</font>

292
00:19:47,110 --> 00:19:48,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's about it.</font>

293
00:19:53,400 --> 00:19:55,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's more than enough.</font>

294
00:19:56,740 --> 00:19:57,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

295
00:19:58,030 --> 00:20:00,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't have any advice to give.</font>

296
00:20:00,760 --> 00:20:03,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should have no problems 
performing any torture.</font>

297
00:20:03,090 --> 00:20:04,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

298
00:20:07,640 --> 00:20:12,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To be honest, I have some 
ideas for torture techniques to try.</font>

299
00:20:12,600 --> 00:20:17,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm worried that my torture target 
won't be able to appreciate them.</font>

300
00:20:17,610 --> 00:20:19,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have no self-confidence.</font>

301
00:20:20,290 --> 00:20:24,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vanilla-senpai, you're always 
so cool and full of confidence.</font>

302
00:20:25,760 --> 00:20:29,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Cool and full of confidence?!</i></font>

303
00:20:31,760 --> 00:20:33,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

304
00:20:39,930 --> 00:20:42,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't tell anyone else...</font>

305
00:20:42,300 --> 00:20:45,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I lack self-confidence as well.</font>

306
00:20:45,430 --> 00:20:46,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

307
00:20:46,920 --> 00:20:49,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always get nervous before torture,</font>

308
00:20:49,900 --> 00:20:52,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and a lot of times, 
I want to cry because I mess up.</font>

309
00:20:54,350 --> 00:20:55,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

310
00:20:55,610 --> 00:20:59,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Recently, I managed to make a f-friend...</font>

311
00:21:00,280 --> 00:21:03,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's always really cool.</font>

312
00:21:03,760 --> 00:21:06,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seeing her makes me want to try hard.</font>

313
00:21:06,700 --> 00:21:09,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Instead of running away 
because I lack confidence...</font>

314
00:21:10,020 --> 00:21:15,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I decided to challenge myself 
to gain the confidence I lack!</font>

315
00:21:15,870 --> 00:21:17,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vanilla-senpai...</font>

316
00:21:19,440 --> 00:21:21,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

317
00:21:21,750 --> 00:21:23,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll challenge myself, too!</font>

318
00:21:23,770 --> 00:21:26,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll give it a shot and 
see what I can do!</font>

319
00:21:26,040 --> 00:21:28,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah! Let's both give it our all!</font>

320
00:21:30,260 --> 00:21:32,970
<font size="20"><font size="15"><b><font color="#1a191c">{\an8}Give it your all!</font></b></font></font>

321
00:23:04,750 --> 00:23:06,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh right, Princess.</font>

322
00:23:07,200 --> 00:23:11,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next week, our new recruit will be 
performing her first torture.</font>

323
00:23:11,330 --> 00:23:14,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? The recruit you keep talking about?</font>

324
00:23:14,760 --> 00:23:17,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of torture will it be?</font>

325
00:23:17,460 --> 00:23:19,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't wait for next week.</font>

326
00:23:22,010 --> 00:23:24,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It still makes me nervous!</font>

327
00:23:26,500 --> 00:23:32,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't told so that I could 
focus on my own torture...</font>

328
00:23:32,130 --> 00:23:35,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I wonder what my 
torture target is like.</font>

329
00:23:35,620 --> 00:23:37,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No point dwelling on it, I guess.</font>

330
00:23:42,450 --> 00:23:43,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Time to give it my all!</font>

